Dorothy Vernon (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Vernon_(actress) 0 Dorothy Vernon (November 11, 1875 – October 28, 1970) was a German-born American film actress. Born Dorothy Baird, she appeared in 131 films between 1919 and 1956. She died in Granada Hills, California from heart disease, aged 94. Her son was actor and entertainer Bobby Vernon.
